{"word":"πάνδικος","slug":"πάνδικος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πάνδικος</b></el> <el>(πάν-δῐκος, ον,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:δίκη'><el>δίκη</el></a>\n<p/><i>all righteous</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b> <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-κως</el>, <i>most justly</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>; but simply = <a href='S:πάντως'><el>πάντως</el></a>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/>"}]}